<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="anywhere-adv">anywhere <strong><em>adv</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /'eniweə(r)/    美 /'eniwer/  </p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.★ <strong>在 / 去任何地方：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>He’s never been anywhere outside Britain.
他从未去过英国以外的任何地方。</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Did you go anywhere interesting for your paid annual holiday?
你有没有去什么好玩的地方休带薪年假？</p></div>

<h4 id="2">2.★ <strong>无论何处；随便哪个地方：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>There are times when people are so tired that they fall asleep almost anywhere.
有时候人们太累了，几乎在哪儿都能睡着。</p><footer>2011 全国</footer></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Rome has tried to protect fish more than <strong>anywhere else</strong> in the world.
罗马比世界上其他任何地方都努力保护鱼类。</p></div>

<h2 id="_2">固定搭配</h2>
<h3 id="anywhere-between-and-from-to">anywhere between … and … / from … to …</h3>
<p>1.<strong>在…到…之间 / 从…到…：</strong>  </p>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>As a tutor you could expect to be paid anywhere between 100 yuan and 200 yuan per hour.
作为一名家教，你有望得到每小时100到200元的报酬。</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>The training can last anywhere from one to six years.
该训练能持续一到六年。</p><footer>2010 湖南改</footer></div>

<h2 id="_3">真题解析</h2>
<ol>
<li>I think Mrs. Stark could be anywhere <strong><em>_</em></strong> 50 and 60 years of age.  （2014 全国改）  </li>
<li>Since people are fond of humor, it is as welcome in conversation as <strong><em>_</em></strong>_ else.  （2011 浙江）<br />
A.anything<br />
B.something<br />
C.anywhere<br />
D.somewhere  </li>
</ol>
<p>答案：
1. between  2. C  </p></div>